  "lemmas": {
    "OPEN": {
      "name": "OPEN_sparse_regime_T_bound",
      "statement": "In the sparse regime t \u226a p (deployed n'/p \u2248 5.555e-04, e=67472, k=17), prove T=\u2205 or |T|\u2264H2=77291948627. CAS: e\u22654 empty on p\u223c10^4 toys; e=3 still has rare T>0 at k=17.",
      "status": "OPEN"
    },
    "phi": {
      "name": "phi_fibre_formulation_of_multipads",
      "proof": [
        "Monic f_\u03b2=X^e+a_{e\u22121}X^{e\u22121}+\u22ef+a_1 X+\u03b2 has root r \u21d4 \u03c6_a(r)=\u03b2.",
        "If |\u03c6_a^{\u22121}(\u03b2)\u2229S|=e then f_\u03b2 splits completely on that fibre (deg e, e roots) \u21d2 that fibre is a free-1 e-set of high a.",
        "\u22652 such \u03b2 \u21d2 multipad high; terminal value in a fibre \u21d2 contributes to T."
      ],
      "statement": "Let S \u2282 F be the arc values, |S|=t. For a=(a_{e\u22121},\u2026,a_1) set \u03c6_a(r)=\u2212(r^e+a_{e\u22121}r^{e\u22121}+\u22ef+a_1 r). Multipad free-1 highs are exactly those a for which \u03c6_a has \u22652 fibres of cardinality e in S. T corresponds to a with an e-fibre containing the terminal value and \u22651 other e-fibre.",
      "status": "PROVED"
    },
    "power_sums": {
      "name": "free1_iff_power_sums_char_gt_e",
      "proof": [
        "Newton: k e_k = sum_{i=1}^k (\u22121)^{i\u22121} e_{k\u2212i} p_i for k < e.",
        "Triangular in either direction with pivots 1..e\u22121 invertible if char > e.",
        "Deployed p = 2^31\u22122^24+1 \u226b e = 67472."
      ],
      "statement": "For e-sets of field elements in char 0 or char p > e, equal monic highs (e_1..e_{e\u22121}) are equivalent to equal power sums p_1..p_{e\u22121} via Newton\u2013Girard (triangular, diagonal k \u2260 0).",
      "status": "PROVED",
      "toys": "Sage: multipad partitions by monic high equal those by power sums (e=3)."
    },
    "trivial": {
      "name": "T_empty_when_t_lt_2e",
      "proof": [
        "|F_H| \u2264 floor(t/e) < 2 for every high."
      ],
      "statement": "If t < 2e then T = \u2205 (no multipad packing).",
      "status": "PROVED"
    }
  },
